        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A very safe two-on-two-off position.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Running the dog walk beautifully.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Leapt right over the contact zone! That's a five-point fault.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The judge's hand goes up. Missed the contact.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Incredible acceleration up the ramp.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
