        priority: 50
      - text: The handler decelerates perfectly to ensure the dog hits the yellow
          zone.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A bit cautious over the apex, bleeding a few tenths of a second.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Absolutely flawless execution on the A-frame.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The dog drives up the A-frame with tremendous power.
        announcerType: 0
