      - text: This dog has mastered the contact zones. Years of practice evident.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The judge signals. Clean contact confirmed.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A perfect run through the contact obstacles so far.
        announcerType: 0
