  finishLinePool:
    state: 7
    arthurPool:
      sourceLines:
      - text: Over the final jump and across the line!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Stops the clock at a spectacular time.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A completely clean run. A masterclass in agility.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: They will be thrilled with that performance.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Unfortunately, those faults will keep them off the podium today.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Let's look at the replay of that front cross.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A valiant effort, but just a fraction off the pace.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The crowd is on their feet!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That is why they are the defending champions.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Thank you for joining us for this magnificent display of canine athleticism.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A new personal best! What a run!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The clock stops. An incredible time!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The handler celebrates. They've earned it.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A flawless finish. Nothing left on the table.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The dog crosses the line, tail wagging. A job well done.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: What a way to end the competition!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A clean run under pressure. Championship material.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The crowd erupts. They witnessed something special.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That time will be hard to beat.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A moment of pure joy. Handler and dog embrace.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: They've done it. A new course record!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A photo finish. The timers confirm the result.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The dog knows. He's celebrating too.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A textbook finish. Every obstacle executed perfectly.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The handlers shake hands. Respect among competitors.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: What a tournament this has been!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A fitting end to an incredible day of agility.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The dog takes a bow. A true champion.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: We've witnessed history today.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A run that will be remembered for years to come.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The final standings are in. What a competition!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A clean sweep. Dominant performance.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The crowd shows their appreciation. Well deserved.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A masterclass from start to finish.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That's how you close out a tournament.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A legendary run. We are honored to have witnessed it.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The dog is the star today. And rightly so.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: A beautiful ending to a beautiful competition.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: The team celebrates. They've achieved the impossible.
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Thank you, and goodnight from the agility arena!
        announcerType: 0
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
