    buckPool:
      sourceLines:
      - text: He did it! Does he get a giant novelty check? Dogs love chewing on
          cardboard.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I'm exhausted just watching that. Arthur, carry me to the car.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: You know, at the end of the day, it's just a wolf running over a piece
          of wood.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I wonder what that dog's going to do to celebrate. Probably drink out
          of the toilet.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: 'Arthur, tell the truth: Are any of these dogs wearing a wire? It feels
          rigged.'
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I'm going down to the floor to see if I can adopt the loser. I like
          an underdog.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Goodnight everyone! Remember to spay and neuter your commentators!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That dog just won! Do they get a trophy? Please tell me it's shaped
          like a bone.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I'm crying, Arthur. Those are happy tears. And maybe a little allergies.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: If I had a dog like that, I'd never need a gym membership. Just play
          fetch!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Arthur, that dog just made more money than I made all year. Can I be
          a dog?
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I need to go lie down. That was too much excitement for one human.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That dog is going to have the best dinner tonight. Steak and everything!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I just witnessed perfection. And I don't say that lightly. I once ate
          a perfect pizza.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Arthur, can we get that dog a cape? He's a superhero!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I think I'm going to adopt a dog now. This is all your fault, agility.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That dog has more followers than me. And I have a great Instagram.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I want to party with that dog. He knows how to celebrate!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: If that dog ever runs for office, he has my vote. Unanimous!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I'm going to tell everyone I was here. Nobody will believe me, but
          that's okay.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That dog deserves a movie deal. 'The Fast and the Furriest.' Coming
          to theaters!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Arthur, I'm going to name my firstborn after that dog. Don't judge
          me.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I just realized something. That dog is better at life than I am.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: If the Olympics need a new sport, this is it. Agility. Let's make it
          happen!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I need a commemorative T-shirt. 'I watched [Dog's Name] win the championship.'
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That dog just inspired me to get off the couch. Maybe tomorrow.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I'm going to have dreams about that run. Good dreams. Happy dreams.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: Arthur, we need to have a watch party for the next tournament. I'll
          bring the jerky.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: That dog has changed my life. I'm a different person now.
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I want to send that dog a fruit basket. Does that work for dogs?
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
      - text: I think I just found my new favorite sport. Move over, bowling!
        announcerType: 1
        voiceIdOverride: 
        tags: []
        priority: 50
